    <h1>Swagger Definition Objects</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h3 id=3D"SwaggerDefinitionObjects-ThreeTypesofSwaggerDefinitions">=
Three Types of Swagger Definitions</h3>
<h3 id=3D"SwaggerDefinitionObjects-"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-fil=
