);"><span>General structure to capture the </span>errors that are returned =
from an API&nbsp;</span></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><co=
de class=3D"js plain" style=3D"text-align: left;">{</code><br><code class=
